snippet.title: The Intermine Legacy: I am the Darkness GAMEPLAY TRAILER
snippet.description:
At long last, here is the GAMEPLAY TRAILER for CHAOS TEXTURE's upcoming visual novel, THE INTERMINE LEGACY: I AM THE DARKNESS. If you'd like more information, consider following us on your social platform of choice (Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, Tumblr), or bookmark our website (http://chaostexture.carrd.co).

CHAOS TEXTURE is:
James David Herd / pixcelation: Creative Director
A Sleepy Witch's Atelier: Art Director
Kiba Walker: Casting Director

Matthew Wilson: Marketing / Social Media
Brent Maldonado: Marketing / Social Media
